{
  "texts": [
    "It achieves nearly human-level performance in tasks such as question answering (Krause & Stolzenburg, 2023) and has demonstrated the ability to pass some of the most challenging exams at Wharton Business School with grades ranging from B to B- (Terwiesch, 2023).",
    "These examples highlight the impressive capabilities of these new LLMs.",
    "While there are other LLMs available, the core reasons for ChatGPT's success are its public accessibility, ease of use, and exceptional versatility across numerous applications and tasks.",
    "Although the foundational language model continues to evolve, our focus is on the free version of ChatGPT.",
    "ChatGPT is both an LLM and an example of generative AI (GenAI)."
  ]
}